Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:08.08,Sign,,0000,0000,0100,,{\bord0\blur0.5\fs75\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\fnBurst My Bubble KK\b1}Fill the Blue Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.59,0:00:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A massive Roman Army\Ncontingent has appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the Seize-No Man's Land border?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that gunshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.44,0:00:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've secured a Roman soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now rendezvous with the\N1st and 3rd divisions on the border-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move and I'll shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:00:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel, please escort your\Nmen outside the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Betrayal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.60,0:01:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girls took our commander hostage\Nand barricaded themselves in the fort!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, it missed her internal organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, for the moment, she should be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be a sacrifice to start the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd be worth less to us dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the last month, we've followed the\Napproaching Roman army from the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably nothing more than a display of power\Nto give them an advantage in the peace talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must think we're fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:02:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Archduke insisted we do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we needed something to\Npush them to attack us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a sobbing POW executed\Nright in front of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't intend to-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The peace talks are a farce!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rome must be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Noël Kannagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, my dear ally, the witch of Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought I wouldn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just used her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël, you have something to do\Nwith the Invisible Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Invisible Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl there was one of the greatest\Ngeniuses in academic history,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the one who revived the Invisible Reaper,\Nan old-era bioweapons plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your talent is still valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha, toss him in the\Nunderground distillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My comrades are already deploying\Nto fight the Romans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One small spark is all that's needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to the battlefield, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was finally over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've both got crap for luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've locked the Colonel inside the distillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have something to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some cookies I got at Treize!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi, you're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave if it gets dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Maidens are supposed\Nto protect the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting them involved in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was hiding, I asked Aisha about\Nthe legend of the Flame Maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she said that the Romans tell\Na totally different legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Maidens protect others' lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't trust you out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, can you even\Nfire a gun at anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I think it's the right thing\Nto do, I might be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fortress maiden, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like our forerunners, the Flame Maidens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe that arbitrary\NRoman fairy tale?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels right to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Maidens protect others' lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that just might be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:06:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how good her ears are,\Nshe can't hear you from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A signal to stop fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I heard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to be happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might have imagined it,\Nand even if not,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't know it means the\Npeace talks are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need to tell Colonel Hopkins-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to take food to the\NColonel, and he was gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We strike in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think they'll listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's worth a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Colonel was laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he saw my Reaper\Nkill all those people,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was laughing so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll kill... He'll fight until no one is left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I helped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think that, then save more\Nlives than you've taken, Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cease-fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But her ears are that good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll vouch for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a tiny kid, and she forgets stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and isn't sexy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest everyone here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want war that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,War advances civilization and science.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:08:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to bring back the glory\Nhumanity once had.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Romans are going to attack\Ntomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, there's no way to stop the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi was arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Demon of Vingt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to deliver the\Nsound I've been given!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you make that decision yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone was saying the world is ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love the people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha was saying the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a soldier, I have killed people, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...just like...you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have suffered enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have suffered enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So even if no one else forgives you, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So even if...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Aisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do this, there'll be no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're OK with that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I've got nothing else to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For our sakes, you've always said\Nwhat you thought was best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a girl my age\Nto be tortured, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Rio's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Noël and Kanata are such slackers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought I had to work harder...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm such a bad captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May all of the Gods grant their\Nblessings to the Flame Maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Primary converter reactor output rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FAP, FAC, DMR, ECP all normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superconductor circuit functioning\Nwithin stable parameters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire control system's looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Primary and secondary cannons are online!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release all joint locks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Weight reduction system online.\NCoefficient is around five.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we just do it like in training, we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, my girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Load AP round!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AP round loaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kana, the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Begin the attack"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemikazuchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:14:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've restored so much of that\Nancient high technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact all tanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do everything you can to stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want any more war!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to take us out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon of Vingt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Circle around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet up with the forces to our rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Maidens protect others' lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is in your hands, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before the world became as it is now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God sent an angel to punish the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The angel was wounded, and set his wings\Ndown to rest, at a western-end town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the maidens, who lived in the\Ncity's fortress, that saved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was sent to destroy them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they took pity on his wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaining the help of a giant spider,\Nthey gave the angel refuge at the bottom of the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each, in turn, embraced the angel's neck,\Nto keep the blood from pouring out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, he gave them a golden horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:16:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But eventually, the townspeople found\Nhim there. They set fire to the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning the maidens, and\Ntaking the angel's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legend says that then armies\Nof angels appeared, covering the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then a miracle occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A glorious sound filled the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the angels left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last maiden had used her last breath\Nto sound the golden horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you remember that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one you gave the caramel to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be caught up in this, too, won't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All troops, prepare to charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an allied tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's with...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 1121 Platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cease-fire signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Roman military signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stop here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready the main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... They won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kana!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both sides, lay down your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am second heir to the royal line of Helvetia
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and fiancée to the Holy Roman Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio Kazumiya Arkadia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I command you by the names of my father,\Nthe Archduke of Helvetia, and of the Roman Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The peace talks have ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is to be no more fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:21:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both sides are to disband immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a royal order!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who disobey will be punished by
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the first Helvetia Royal Guard,\Nin both leaders' names!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:21:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring sure has sprung.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noël,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.84,0:22:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that letter Aisha sent you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.19,0:22:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wounds are healed, and I'm practicing\Nthe trumpet every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Translate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's doing well and practicing her trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, we get letters from Rome\Nbut not from the capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a princess now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even on the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was surrounded by guards,\Nand we couldn't talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear Claus' bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here! She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.87,0:23:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you how much I've been\Nlooking forward to the new girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.33,0:23:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be really hard-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Lt. Rio Kazumiya Arkadia. I have been transferred\Nto the 1121 Platoon as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.98,0:23:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Filicia Heidemann, please\Ngive me permission to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:23:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't use ranks here, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.97,0:24:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Roman Emperor is actually a decent guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.87,0:24:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd grant any wish I had,\Nas a reward for stopping the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.25,0:24:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.61,0:24:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.90,0:24:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Rio.
